# --- Scripts: DB / Supabase / R2 (configure in .env.local, not committed) ---
# db:test, db:apply, supabase:backup, audit:supabase:* → PRODUCTS_DATABASE_URL or DATABASE_URL + Supabase keys above
# assets:cdn:*, assets:r2:* → CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID, CLOULDFLARE_S3_URL, CLOULD_ACCESS_KEY_ID, CLOULDFLARE_S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
# assets:r2:count → optional CLOUDFLARE_R2_CATALOG_BUCKET (default oando-asset-cdn)
# screenshot:planner → dev server at http://localhost:3000 (no extra env)
# inventory:app-pages, inventory:scripts → no credentials; write under results/
